.000Z","msg":"第一題c係咪直接代番a,b題既m+sd入<br />\nm+0.1sd 跟住睇下邊個細就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59dcb080123e146278d1962354c870248c452f9c","tid":148471,"uid":24378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:06:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Part b 答案係零</blockquote><br />\nb因為話要exactly所以係0?</blockquote><br />\n係 對於continuous distribution，任何prob being an exact value都係0"},{"pid":"e426f2d1b1f244abf6091538a915ea70bbc5487c","tid":148471,"uid":24378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>statistics功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打我都唔識呢條<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />星期5交</blockquote><br />\n巴打可以既話教我做a<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec94bc42a11f9ab0802cb38386bf80aa36072d0","tid":148471,"uid":10603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:33:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一題c係咪直接代番a,b題既m+sd入<br />\nm+0.1sd 跟住睇下邊個細就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好明目張膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該係"},{"pid":"cfefa290f3ec424063cc42ba670a7d7038da46c2","tid":148471,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T01:43:50.000Z","msg":"點解好似見過人問"},{"pid":"2ca220bcf2037e6c073b1f83cc30a1035f95ce34","tid":148471,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T04:30:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Part b 答案係零</blockquote><br />\nb因為話要exactly所以係0?</blockquote><br />\n係 對於continuous distribution，任何prob being an exact value都係0</blockquote><br />\n題目都冇講continuous"},{"pid":"1ede1966009ae1a0603b2f200274cecc5c75e02a","tid":148471,"uid":25065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:52:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d535620e01c8c2cd6f5f13d5a4329fe833be1cdc","tid":148471,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:02:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Part b 答案係零</blockquote><br />\nb因為話要exactly所以係0?</blockquote><br />\n係 對於continuous distribution，任何prob being an exact value都係0</blockquote><br />\n題目都冇講continuous</blockquote><br />\nSample mean distribution is normal for some n&gt;N<br />\n同個sample本身distribution係咪continuous無關係</blockquote><br />\nsample mean distribution唔會係normal㗎喎，除非本身啲sample係normal<br />\n最多話佢approximately normal"},{"pid":"4a2bc2df0430cb0b5a85be50e9e33a8b3f19bc55","tid":148471,"uid":8550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:11:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Part b 答案係零</blockquote><br />\nb因為話要exactly所以係0?</blockquote><br />\n係 對於continuous distribution，任何prob being an exact value都係0</blockquote><br />\n題目都冇講continuous</blockquote><br />\nGiven 咗sample size &gt; 50<br />\n所以by central limit thm , it is also a normal distribution <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80238a90cf3e740b9f78bd7be3028c225cd1d25","tid":148471,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:27:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Part b 答案係零</blockquote><br />\nb因為話要exactly所以係0?</blockquote><br />\n係 對於continuous distribution，任何prob being an exact value都係0</blockquote><br />\n題目都冇講continuous</blockquote><br />\nGiven 咗sample size &gt; 50<br />\n所以by central limit thm , it is also a normal distribution <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經答咗，呢個情況最多只可以話好接近normal,而唔係真係normal,除非啲sample係normally distributed"},{"pid":"2f7a36cb78224c9553464bc5f64a0084bdc312ff","tid":148471,"uid":40745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:31:42.000Z","msg":"樓主中幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}